455
00:56:33.158 --> 00:56:34.951
- og få dem sat i sving!

456
00:56:35.076 --> 00:56:38.079
Tiden er knap! Kom i gang!

457
00:57:07.817 --> 00:57:08.985
Aurora...

458
00:57:10.069 --> 00:57:11.571
